OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,FWeighing 45 stone with his kidneys
OL,7,Ffailing, Ioan Pollard from Caernarfon
OL,8,Fdidn't know if he would live to see
OL,9,Fthe morning.
OL,11,FThe 27-year-old needed a transplant,
OL,12,Fbut due to his weight, he was
OL,13,Fineligible to be on the waiting list.
OL,15,F"I had no self-control. Food
OL,16,Fcontrolled everything I did and how I
OL,17,Flived my life.
