OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,F"At the time, I didn't accept that I
OL,7,Fwas addicted to food and was
OL,8,Fovereating. But, looking back, I
OL,9,Fobviously was," says Ioan on a
OL,10,Fprogramme on S4C, 'Marw Isio Byw'
OL,11,F('Dying to Live').
OL,13,FAt university and through his twenties
OL,14,FIoan's weight increased dramatically,
OL,15,Fand his health consequently
OL,16,Fdeteriorated, and a month after his
OL,17,F27th birthday, he almost lost his life.
