OL,6,F"I think I really pushed myself as far
OL,7,Fas I could in terms of how much my
OL,8,Fbody could take. The hospital staff
OL,9,Ftold me that the next eight hours were
OL,10,Fcritical and that I may not be here in
OL,11,Fthe morning."
OL,13,FIoan had minor grazes on his legs
OL,14,Fwhich had turned septic.
