OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,F"It was immediately obvious that my
OL,7,Fkidneys had been severely damaged.
OL,8,FThey told me that things didn't look
OL,9,Fgood and that we needed to start
OL,10,Ftalking about dialysis. The size and
OL,11,Fweight of my body meant I had no
OL,12,Fchance of getting a transplant. The
OL,13,Ftruth is, I was far too fat."
OL,15,FHis family and friends were very
OL,16,Fworried about him, especially his
OL,17,Fmother.
OL,19,FEleri Pollard said: "I was worried
OL,20,Fabout his health. I thought he was
OL,21,Fgoing to eat himself to the grave."
