OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,FLooking back at his clothes from this
OL,7,Fperiod, Ioan's waist measured almost
OL,8,Fsix feet, and he had to buy special
OL,9,Fclothes that would fit him.
OL,11,F"I could be here all day blaming this
OL,12,Fand that for the situation I was in,
OL,13,Fbut it simply comes down to two things
OL,14,F- I was too greedy and too lazy."
OL,16,F"When I look back, I feel embarrassed
OL,17,Fthat I had chosen to live my life like
OL,18,Fthat. It's only now that I realise
OL,19,Fwhat I'd done to myself and my body."
