OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,FOver a period of seven years, Ioan
OL,7,Flost over half his weight. He
OL,8,Funderwent bariatric surgery to reduce
OL,9,Fhis stomach and remove excess skin. 30
OL,10,Fstone lighter, he was finally
OL,11,Fconsidered eligible for a transplant.
OL,13,F'Grateful'
OL,15,FIoan's mother was beyond grateful when
OL,16,Fshe found out she was a match and
OL,17,Fcould donate one of her kidneys to her
OL,18,Fson: "I want Ioan to live his life, he
OL,19,Fdeserves it."
