OL,3,CMan lost 30 stone for life changing
OL,4,Ctransplant
OL,6,FNow, 35 years of age and recovering
OL,7,Ffrom a kidney transplant, Ioan is
OL,8,Fhoping for a healthier future.
OL,10,F"I've been through so much. I just
OL,11,Fwant this to work without any
OL,12,Fproblems. "I've lived a sheltered life
OL,13,Fwhile carrying all that weight, being
OL,14,Fhere now reminds me how fragile life
OL,15,Fis.
OL,17,F"My mum has given me such a gift and
OL,18,Fit's so important now that I respect
OL,19,Fthat gift."
